    "6127149": {
      "title": "Correlated mRNAs and miRNAs from co-expression and regulatory networks affect porcine muscle and finally meat properties",
      "abstract": "Physiological processes aiding the conversion of muscle to meat involve many genes associated with muscle structure and metabolic processes. MicroRNAs regulate networks of genes to orchestrate cellular functions, in turn regulating phenotypes."
